title: Cuisinart Griddler
description: The 4 in 1 Cuisinart Griddler makes cooking great meals in 15 minutes or less, a snap.

asset.author: CuisinartVideo
asset.hookText: The 4 in 1 Cuisinart Griddler makes cooking great meals in 15 minutes or less, a snap. See more at http://thegriddler.com/

transcripts:
[MUSIC PLAYING]
You may think there is no way to cook a great meal in 15 minutes, but Cuisinart has four ways in one pretty amazing appliance. The Griddler, It's a nonstick contact grill. A wide open grill. The perfect panini press and an extra large griddle. A real multitask. Breakfast, lunch, dinner and endless variety of delicious meals. The only thing easier is cleaning it. The four in one from Cuisinart makes cooking great meals in 15 minutes or less a snap.
